"""
VUAA / UPP — Regional Policy & Ordinance Tracker
================================================
Tracks municipal legislation (ordinances, resolutions, zoning cases, etc.)
across metro Phoenix and flags items touching four advocacy priorities:
Housing, Heat mitigation, Transit, and Walkability.

This is the COMPANION to the meetings tracker. The meetings tracker answers
"what's on the agenda this week"; this answers "what's actually moving through
the pipeline, and where does it stand."

v1 data source: Legistar Web API (the cities below expose it). New cities /
platforms slot in by adding an adapter that yields the same record shape.

Run:  python3 track.py
Out:  ./site/index.html, ./site/ordinances.json, ./site/digest.txt
"""

